Subject: Getting multiple reports of users not able to get policy to client machine
Description:
We are receiving multiple reports of users not receiving the policy and their devices are being blocked.

we are Wave 4 of a multi wave deployment and incidents started happening last week.

last seen date is 10/10/2024 but the users are currently logged on and device is showing as blocked from today which is 10/14/2024.

Need urgent assistance
Next_Steps__c: Resolved, RCA sent, need to confirm closure with customer in weekly meeting
Solution_Comment__c: Root cause was full server disk caused by misconfigured web access log.  RCA provided.
